1
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:33,640
Shen Zhixia, Lu Jingheng,

2
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:36,479
why do you two get to be fine?

3
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,920
Zhixia! Zhixia!

4
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:56,890
How are you, Zhixia?

5
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,520
Ambulance! Ambulance!

6
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,930
Ambulance! Call an ambulance!

7
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:27,520
Dad, I won!

8
00:02:28,079 --> 00:02:30,120
You are the best, sweetie.

9
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:34,320
Zhixia.

10
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:35,320
Stand up.

11
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,520
What regrets?

12
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:39,240
Who should I settle scores with?

13
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:43,840
Thank you for putting so much effort for me.

14
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,760
I know you're very tired.

15
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:48,760
But you can't fall down now.

16
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:52,280
The person who killed the original owner is among them.

17
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:20,440
Divorce.

18
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:22,040
Let's divorce right now.

19
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,160
Don't you want to go back?

20
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:32,760
Stand up.

21
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:49,240
Stand up.

22
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,160
Survive.

23
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:59,760
Stand up and survive.

24
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,680
Doctor, how is she?

25
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:43,170
Shen Zhixia, you're awake.

26
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:47,260
Does it hurt anywhere?

27
00:04:48,440 --> 00:04:49,680
I feel much better.

28
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:52,720
If Su Yuran were right here,

29
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:55,120
I could punch her twice.

30
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,680
You get some rest.

31
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:04,140
I'll go get the doctor.

32
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:10,520
Aunt,

33
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:13,580
you're the only one who can save me this time.

34
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:14,800
If Lu Jingheng

35
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,120
refuses to let this go,

36
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:19,040
I'll be done for, Aunt.

37
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:22,140
I've already been to the hospital twice.

38
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:24,240
But he wouldn't even let me in the door.

39
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:26,200
He insists on having you prosecuted.

40
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,840
What can I do?

41
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:29,080
Are you just going to

42
00:05:29,080 --> 00:05:30,560
stand by and watch them

43
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:32,720
send me to prison, Aunt?

44
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:37,080
All these things were clearly

45
00:05:37,080 --> 00:05:39,280
orchestrated by you and my cousin.

46
00:05:39,280 --> 00:05:40,960
Why is it that now that we're exposed,

47
00:05:40,960 --> 00:05:41,800
you want me to take all the blame

48
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,720
all by myself?

49
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,480
Aunt.

50
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:47,120
Now that I'm in trouble,

51
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:49,240
you can't just abandon me, Aunt.

52
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,200
How dare you even mention it?

53
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:53,360
Kicking you out of the Lu family

54
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,890
was just a stalling tactic.

55
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:56,159
Once your uncle calms down,

56
00:05:56,159 --> 00:05:58,240
I would have found a way to bring you back.

57
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,240
But look at you.

58
00:06:00,280 --> 00:06:02,680
You were stupid enough to run someone over.

59
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,400
Aunt.

60
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:08,040
I was stupid this time.

61
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:09,080
It was my fault.

62
00:06:09,080 --> 00:06:11,120
But could you please help me one more time?

63
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,800
If you don't help me this time,

64
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,720
I'll be out of options, Aunt.

65
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:16,120
Don't grab me.

66
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:19,880
Aunt.

67
00:06:19,880 --> 00:06:22,120
Just one last time, okay, Aunt?

68
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,160
Please help me again.

69
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:24,520
I'm begging you.

70
00:06:32,159 --> 00:06:32,960
Fine.

71
00:06:35,400 --> 00:06:37,280
You're not going to help me anymore, are you?

72
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:38,000
Then wait until I expose

73
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:40,400
everything you and my cousin have done

74
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:42,080
to Uncle.

75
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,960
Don't blame me for being ruthless.

76
00:06:46,960 --> 00:06:47,720
Aunt.

77
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,520
Hello.

78
00:07:25,080 --> 00:07:25,760
Okay.

79
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:27,920
I hope you can keep your word.

80
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:30,490
I will book a flight back immediately.

81
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:40,760
Hello,

82
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:42,760
which room is Mrs. Lu in?

83
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:45,880
On the left, VIP section 1208.

84
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,120
Thank you.

85
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,240
Jingheng really cares about his wife.

86
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:57,040
No wonder the nurses outside are all praising him.

87
00:07:58,520 --> 00:08:00,520
Actually, my injury isn't serious this time.

88
00:08:00,520 --> 00:08:01,280
It's just that he

89
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:02,560
likes to make a fuss.

90
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:04,380
Thank you for coming to see me.

91
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:05,480
The doctor said

92
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,960
you need to eat more fruit.

93
00:08:06,960 --> 00:08:08,040
Take more vitamins

94
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,160
to recover faster.

95
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,440
I've already had a lot.

96
00:08:12,400 --> 00:08:13,400
Actually, I came here today,

97
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:14,360
besides visiting you,

98
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,160
there's another thing

99
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,820
I want to discuss with you two.

100
00:08:18,960 --> 00:08:20,840
Although you kept a low profile this time,

101
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:23,120
there are already rumors spreading around.

102
00:08:23,120 --> 00:08:24,040
I think,

103
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:26,280
instead of becoming a topic for gossip,

104
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:28,360
it's better to take the initiative and do an exclusive interview.

105
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:29,040
For one,

106
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:31,280
it can consolidate our previous PR effects.

107
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:32,080
For another,

108
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,159
it can also change

109
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:35,960
the public's old impression of my sister-in-law.

110
00:08:36,799 --> 00:08:38,200
The process is not complicated.

111
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,200
I'll ask the director to record

112
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,400
your daily recovery routine.

113
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:41,929
Keep it as real as possible.

114
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:45,360
But Zhixia needs to rest now.

115
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:46,600
Just ignore him.

116
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,280
I told you,

117
00:08:47,280 --> 00:08:48,080
he likes

118
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:49,680
to make a fuss over nothing.

119
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:51,160
Since you said it's for our own good,

120
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:52,220
let's just film it.

121
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:56,120
Sit a bit closer to the light later.

122
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,080
That way, the light on your face

123
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,120
will be softer.

124
00:08:59,920 --> 00:09:01,160
Is the equipment ready?

125
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:01,920
The equipment is fine.

126
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:02,960
We can start now.

127
00:09:03,280 --> 00:09:04,610
Then let's get started.

128
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,160
Mr. Lu.

129
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,520
You're here so early today.

130
00:09:19,520 --> 00:09:20,880
What delicious food did you make this time?

131
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:21,720
The usual.

132
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:23,960
But Mrs. Lu is busy right now.

133
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:26,360
Miss Wen brought some people over for an interview.

134
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,680
I guess she'll have to eat a bit later.

135
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,640
It's fine.

136
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:31,320
I can heat it up after she's done.

137
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,780
Okay, I'll leave you to it.

138
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,200
Mrs. Lu.

139
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:38,800
We've asked a lot just now,

140
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:40,080
but what everyone cares about the most

141
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:42,080
is when you had the car accident.

142
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:44,200
Why did you choose to risk your life?

143
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:46,320
Actually, I can't explain it clearly.

144
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:49,400
Probably because in many moments when I was helpless,

145
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:51,080
he stood in front of me

146
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:54,000
and shielded me from a lot of danger and trouble.

147
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:55,280
So at that moment,

148
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:56,280
all I wanted

149
00:09:56,280 --> 00:09:58,720
was to risk everything and stand in front of him.

150
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:00,720
There are many doubts from the public,

151
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,280
saying your marriage to Mr. Lu is an arranged one

152
00:10:02,280 --> 00:10:03,560
with no real feelings.

153
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:05,560
What are your thoughts on this?

154
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:07,520
Actually, two people being together

155
00:10:07,520 --> 00:10:09,600
might not be because of a passionate romance,

156
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:12,120
but definitely because of an inescapable destiny.

157
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:14,120
You might not believe me if I say this.

158
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:16,360
I often feel like I am in this world,

159
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:18,280
floating in mid-air,

160
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:20,160
my feet not touching the ground,

161
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:23,520
with nothing around me to hold onto.

162
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:26,480
Lu Jingheng is the first

163
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,920
and the only person

164
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:30,800
that makes me feel I have someone to rely on.

165
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,560
I don't know how to describe

166
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:34,000
the feelings between us.

167
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,320
I just want to say

168
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:38,480
that I am truly grateful for him.

169
00:10:38,560 --> 00:10:41,480
Thank him for appearing by my side.

170
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:50,320
The soup is a bit cold.

171
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,560
I'll go heat it up.

172
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:02,320
Miss Wen.

173
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,120
Remember,

174
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,400
the focus of this edit

175
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:10,320
is to pick out all the scenes of Mr. Lu taking care of his wife

176
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,520
and make them stand out.

177
00:11:11,520 --> 00:11:12,800
Include as many of them as possible.

178
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:14,320
Mr. Lu specifically instructed

179
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,200
that this report

180
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,280
is to let everyone see

181
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:17,740
how much he loves his wife.

182
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:20,040
Otherwise, all our efforts over this time

183
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:20,880
will be in vain.

184
00:11:20,880 --> 00:11:21,640
No problem.

185
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:25,360
Let me review it after you finish editing.

186
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,360
Put some heart into it.

187
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:27,120
Okay.

188
00:11:43,880 --> 00:11:45,080
Finished recording?

189
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:46,300
You must be hungry.

190
00:11:46,600 --> 00:11:48,660
I stewed your favorite pork rib soup.

191
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:50,180
I just heated it up.

192
00:11:53,920 --> 00:11:55,360
The recording is over.

193
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:57,280
Why do you still bother doing this?

194
00:11:57,280 --> 00:11:59,360
This has nothing to do with the recording.

195
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:00,560
You haven't fully recovered yet.

196
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:02,090
You need some nourishment.

197
00:12:04,120 --> 00:12:05,580
Have you seen the footage?

198
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:06,880
I have.

199
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,530
It was shot really well.

200
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:10,720
It must have been hard on you

201
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:11,920
to be so cooperative.

202
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:15,400
This is Miss Wen's computer.

203
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,760
Take it back to her.

204
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:20,320
What's wrong?

205
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,560
I'm a little tired and want to sleep for a while.

206
00:12:22,560 --> 00:12:23,490
You can go first.

207
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:27,720
Remember to drink the soup then.

